line 10883: " s:LocalFastBrowser: handles setting up/taking down fast browsing for the local browser {{{2
line 10884: "
line 10885: "     g:netrw_    Directory Is
line 10886: "     fastbrowse  Local  Remote
line 10887: "  slow   0         D      D      D=Deleting a buffer implies it will not be re-used (slow)
line 10888: "  med    1         D      H      H=Hiding a buffer implies it may be re-used        (fast)
