line 10895: "  s:netrw_events : doesn't exist, s:LocalFastBrowser() will install autocmds with medium-speed or fast browsing
line 10896: "                   =1: autocmds installed, but ignore next FocusGained event to avoid initial double-refresh of listing.
line 10897: "                       BufEnter may be first event, then a FocusGained event.  Ignore the first FocusGained event.
line 10898: "                       If :Explore used: it sets s:netrw_events to 2, so no FocusGained events are ignored.
line 10899: "                   =2: autocmds installed (doesn't ignore any FocusGained events)
